I'm sure we can all agree that 2020 was a mess... But your taxes don’t have to be! I’ve partnered with @turbotaxcanada using their Live Full Service to help me make this process as easy as can be. As a freelance photographer, my life is all over the place and so are my finances! 😂
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Due to unusual circumstances I had to spend time and money on a small island abroad for half the year. It became a huge challenge to stay organized since my year didn’t go according to plan. I had to pivot my business and finances to overcome this unexpected marooning once I returned home!
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Using TurboTax Live Full Service and being able to get unlimited tax advice and answers from an expert helped me organize and understand how to properly file my taxes in a cohesive manner during this crazy year... And for years to come! Having a dedicated expert do my taxes for me from start to finish gave me a little lift for being able to get after what I love!
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Whether you’re self-employed, or a regular tax paying individual, TurboTax Live Full Service has REAL experts to help understand your unique tax situation and complete them for you!
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
So what are you waiting for? Get started with TurboTax Live Full Service free up some time to do what matters most.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
#ad #LittleLifts

node.text:
Hi everyone! I am partnering with my friends from @thecheekypanda_uk and we have a message for you that you may not be aware of! Please watch this video to learn more.❤️
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
As we all know, climate change is a very real problem that we are globally facing. One of the easiest ways we can work to prevent this is to start transitioning to sustainably made products that we use everyday. Another way is to limit the amounts of single-use plastic that we use in our daily lives. It's easy, simple and if everyone starts working towards doing our part we will have a much healthier planet to live on. I am in no way preaching and I know I am not perfect myself. However, even if each of us starts making small changes in our lives that will go a lot further than making none at all. A world where everyone is 100% sustainable in every way is a complete longshot at the moment and a HUGE ask... But a world where everyone makes one small change in their lives can go a long way with a global population of 7.8 BILLION+ people...
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
One thing that I am 100% sure that we all use in our day to day lives is... Well... Toilet paper! 😂🧻
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Earth has lost over 28 million acres of forest due to logging for big tissue companies since 1996. Switching to products made from bamboo can help save them since it is the world's fastest growing plant and can be harvested every year! So the question is... Why are we still cutting down trees for our toilet paper? 🌲
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Unfortunately it doesn't just stop there... Please watch this video to learn more about how we are destroying our planet and how sustainably made bamboo products such as @thecheekypanda_uk can help work towards saving it.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
All in all... An easy first step can be to start sustainably wiping our bums! 😂💩🌍🌱
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
#TheCheekyPanda

@chelseamealo and I set out to travel around and photograph Mauritius. We never expected to spend 70 days in lockdown abroad.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
After arriving in Mauritius the world around us began to fall apart, the country closed their airport and we got stuck in a 70-day lockdown.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
During lockdown we passed the time by exploring the island with my drone and heading up the hike in our backyard.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Once the lockdown was lifted we adventures beyond our little backyard paradise ✨
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
I would like to thank my friends from @corona for helping @chelseamealo and I tell the story of our most wild adventure yet ✨
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Now that lockdown has been lifted we have been exploring the beautiful island of Mauritius and have more amazing stories to tell with @corona 💛
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
#AllAboutAdventures

node.text:
The All About Adventures team and I embarked on a treacherous  journey that lead us 4000m up to a campsite that is next to an EXTREMELY active volcano 🌋
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
We were greeted with horrible weather... AKA pouring rain, massive hail and extremely high winds.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
We thought the adventure would be a bust... Until last minute at 3am the weather cleared up and gave us the show of a lifetime.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Here is the behind the scenes footage from the adventure incase you missed my Instagram story! 🤙🏻
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
#AllAboutAdventures

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BRAYDEN | travel + adventure 🗺 in Peru. May be an image of nature.

node.text:
Cordillera Huayhuash… This mountain range in the Peruvian Andes is my all time favourite place on the planet.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
The 7 day trek through these gnarly peaks meant so much to me that I literally got a tattoo of it on my arm 😂

node.text:
Wherever I am in the world I can ASSURE you that I am jamming out to at least one of my speakers from @ultimateears 🎶
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
This summer they set me up with their whole lineup so my friends and I could rock out in Mexicoooo ☀️
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
With the PartyUp feature we were able to sync together the HYPERBOOM, MEGABOOM 3 and BOOM 3 while having a little fiesta in my villa 💃🏻🕺🏼
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
The speakers are also waterproof and VIRTUALLY INDESTRUCTIBLE so if you love to sing in the shower and/or destroy everything you love like me you will for sure dig these things 😂
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Want to snag a speaker of your own? Be sure to follow @ultimateears and show them how you #GoBOOM with their speakers this summer, and you'll have a chance to win one 🎉
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

node.text:
Canada’s borders have officially opened up to the USA as of today. I know this is a controversial topic so I’d love to hear your thoughts!
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
🇨🇦🤝🇺🇸
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
With the precautions in place, I personally believe Canada will remain safe and I am beyond excited that I can see some friends and loved ones with much more ease than it has been for the last year and a bit ❤️

node.text:
The catacombs of Bryce Canyon National park in the winter truly make for an otherworldly landscape 🪐
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
The wild colour palette with snow and red rock + the lack of crowds make this place a photography paradise. But if you go make sure your prepared with the right gear. It’s FREEZING cold and the trail turns into an ice rink so you’ll need to layer up and wear micro-spikes on your feet to keep you secure ⛸❄️

node.text:
🌊 missing you comes in waves 🌊
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Here’s something a weeeeeee bit different than what I usually share on here!
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
@meghanorourkee and I decided to throw a bit of a moody spin on some images we snapped together while driving down the California coast with @brendinkelly and @dgsc.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Although I absolutely LOOOOOVE shooting wild landscapes in far away places, it’s been super fun to slow down and focus on shooting some images that capture a specific feeling in one location.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
I’m super stoked that we were able to make this shoot come to life the way that we imagined it… And had a goood time doing it!
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
We waltzed down the shoreline of one of the most popular locations in California, peeped some wild flowers, had some good laughs with great company and finished the evening off with some brewskis at a bangin’ af brewery.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Cheers to more good times and fantastic adventures 🍻

node.text:
The caption block has been REAL these days. I find myself writing a sentence, rewording it, deleting it and then just STRAIGHT UP giving up 😂
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
I’m currently on the road mooching wifi while in a small town in Idaho preparing to go camp out in the mountains. It’ll be my first overnight hike in awhile and I’m STOOOKED.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Anyways that has nothing to do with this shot that I snapped while flying over Molokai in a helicopter but here we areeeee 🚁
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
P.S. When we turned the corner and saw these massive sea cliffs the pilot started playing the Jurassic Park theme song and it was absolutely maaaagical 🦕
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Well, it looks like I wrote a caption. Time to give myself a pat on the back and go camping 🏕🤠

We had an UNREAL time staying at and adventuring around the architectural masterpiece of a property that @azulik has to offer ☀️
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Around every corner there is some sort of jaw-dropping piece of art to be found and the rooms themselves are out of cooooontroooool!
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Swipe through this series to see the epic villa that I stayed in and to watch @heykelseyj rip it up on the swing on the balcony 🌊
